Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:28.01,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(357,124)}{\pos(218,173)}The Ghouls Attack:\N Their Aim is the Red-Eyes Black Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.18,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Battle City?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:36.29,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That means, tomorrow, Domino City will become a Duel Monsters battle arena?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:37.26,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.83,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be a lot of powerful Duelists coming to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.56,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:46.43,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He didn't tell me, who was number 2 at the Duelist Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:47.57,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:50.94,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oi, Jounouchi! You aren't thinking of attending, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.77,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course I am, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.47,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, what about Shizuka-chan's surgery tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.41,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The surgery is only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:01.45,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even so, I should still be able to make it if I quickly get back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.52,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi, you'll be attending too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:10.96,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course~! But one of the rules in Battle City is the Ante Rule, so I can't afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.69,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ante? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.26,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's betting cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.43,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Betting cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:22.30,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah. The winning player can take one rare card from the \nlosing player.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.20,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?! Rare card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:29.78,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That means... if I lose, this will be taken away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:34.81,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you be alright? Because that card is worth everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:42.75,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just kidding! Don't worry. Red-Eyes is my Goddess of Victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:48.49,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He and I have an unbreakable bond of destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.50,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I keep on winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.50,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll get rare card after rare card...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:58.07,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold it! When a person gets greedy, bad things will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:03.18,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, that's right! There's another requirement to attend this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.64,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.61,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The new Duel Disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:11.38,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kaiba-kun's new version of the Virtual Card Battle Machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:14.15,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}New Duel Disk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.52,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.96,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.09,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.83,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}It really suits you to be on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:26.06,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Like a loser dog unable to stand up after a single loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.44,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}The Duel Disks bring back such bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:35.51,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't have it at my place, but that new card shop that opened recently is selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:38.71,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Great! Anyways, let's go buy it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.72,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I remember it was somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.79,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, could it be a shop around the corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.69,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Great! Let's hurry and go buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:53.13,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.60,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anzu, you know this shop too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.77,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yesterday, I came with the other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.90,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.97,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anzu, thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.41,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My other self seems to have regained some spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:10.41,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what did the other Yugi say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.88,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Battle City stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.01,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.52,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}So he really didn't tell him anything about that drawing or that Ishizu woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.68,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}or anything about yesterday at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.59,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, I still think it's kinda strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:28.26,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm certain the other me wouldn't accept the Ante Rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:32.40,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's got no interest in winning rare cards or betting ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:37.27,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's because these 40 cards are picked out from thousands of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.14,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why all our rare cards can't be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:43.31,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why he believes they can't be used for betting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.81,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:50.58,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I keep thinking the other me is looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.99,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.80,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These are really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:57.86,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Honda, take a look at this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.99,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:04.39,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Yugi will realize soon what the other Yugi is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.97,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Their hearts are too close together to hide anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:09.87,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're comin' in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.04,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:16.58,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, are you selling the new Duel Disks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.95,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, You guys are Duelists looking to attend tomorrow's tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:23.32,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's been a lot of customers like you the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.85,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, may I ask what your names are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.92,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.99,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.23,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.43,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, amazingly strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.60,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:44.54,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kaiba Corporation has the whole country's Duelist's information
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:48.31,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About the Duelist's level and number of rare cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:55.78,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Duelists above level 5 can receive the Duel Disk for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.42,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kaiba-kun has...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:02.82,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really? This way, he could control the contest's standards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:07.19,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi-kun's Duelist level is at the amazing level 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:10.90,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Congratulations! This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.83,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.43,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, I'm Katsuya Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.40,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's see... Jounouchi-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:25.14,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah~ Level 2, Nobody~ What's this "nobody"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.78,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}WHAT?! NOBODY!!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:31.02,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}THAT KAIBA BASTARD!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.05,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.19,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Calm down?! Then what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.89,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.36,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Level 2 is not qualified to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:44.23,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why doesn't the runner up in Duelist Kingdom qualify?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.70,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.87,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}He has such a powerful rare card, this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.41,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I refuse to believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.91,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.31,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The system seems to have malfunctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.78,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you take a look carefully, your at a level 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.82,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You meet the standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.66,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:14.56,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the...? It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:18.23,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then there's no other choice. I'll take the Duel Disk then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.76,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.10,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:23.77,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.00,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a relief, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.17,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.94,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry for interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:37.45,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, it's me. I've found new prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.75,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's this late already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:45.16,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, but I need to go to the hospital. So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:49.16,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope Shizuka-chan's surgery will be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.93,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:51.43,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.63,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's finally time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.94,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then Jounouchi's heart must be really muddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.57,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}His mom also went to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:07.45,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When he was still small, his mom took his sister and left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:13.69,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really? When she's in surgery, he can't avoid seeing his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:17.66,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright!! Tomorrow I need to help connect family relationships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.76,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Isn't that a bit too enthusiastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:24.10,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's because Shizuka-chan is Honda-kun's type.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.94,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In order to get the new Duel Disk, I was slowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.71,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait for me, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:47.45,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?! I'm in a hurry right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.86,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you Katsuya Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.62,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the? You know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:57.63,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We bet everything on the name of the Ghouls. We can't afford to let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:58.96,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Ghouls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.38,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I think I've seen the name in the newspaper before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:04.21,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}They're a group that Duels with Duelists around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.84,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}taking away their rare cards; A thieving organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.55,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.97,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I challenge you to a Duel right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.94,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can I let you guys go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:23.48,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine then... The rules will be the Battle City's rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.94,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course with Ante as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:29.36,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you lose, I'll take your Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.49,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.12,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}There's no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.20,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.79,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Let me take care of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:50.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:55.27,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once I think about the surgery I get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.19,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just now I got a phone call from Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.94,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He says he's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Katsuya is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.45,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.41,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I Summon Panther Warrior in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.62,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.58,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I put this monster in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.80,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll quickly finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.64,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My card is Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:38.60,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This can Special Summon 4 monsters at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.73,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I sacrifice one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.15,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Panther Warrior, Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:57.74,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on now, what's wrong?! Hurry and come at me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:59.33,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:02.08,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Due to Angel's Charity's effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:06.92,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I draw 3 cards, then throw away 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.76,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next, I put this monster in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.05,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:16.56,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}He challenged me to this Duel, but all he's doing is protecting himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:40.54,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Big brother, hurry up and come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:47.96,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know why you keep defending, but I'm not going to loosen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.92,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wyvern Warrior{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.51,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next, I sacrifice 1 Scapegoat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.47,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I use Panther Warrior to attack your set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.40,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.32,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This way, the defending monster is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:14.45,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think the Battle City rules allow you to attack the player directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:17.24,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go, Wyvern Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.74,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.67,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.54,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.13,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Angel's Charity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.09,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:35.76,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I draw 3 cards, and discard 2 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.97,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next, I put this monster in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.89,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Using the same cards again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.56,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:48.31,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,400)}Just now I was thinking what you were planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.57,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the truth is, you're just too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:55.03,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am just too strong, so all you can do is defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.53,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Now I can easily finish this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.41,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Let's see... the new rules say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:06.83,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}In order to summon a 7 star monster, what do I need to sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.46,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Scapegoat can't be used as a Sacrifice Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:14.42,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Panther Warrior and Wyvern Warrior are on my field....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:19.72,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forget it! I got {\i1}more{\i0} than enough sacrifices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:23.18,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I Summon Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:37.40,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's it! In order to summon a 7 star monster I need 2 sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:40.87,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.87,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Fire Bullet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.42,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How's that? Red-Eyes' strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.59,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No wonder you guys want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.72,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't give you this card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:14:00.09,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'll at least show you his coolness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.80,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next, we'll determine the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.56,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.98,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't have it much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.65,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.40,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Draw card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:18.03,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have met my unlucky curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.78,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come out, Exodia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.74,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?! Exodia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.21,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:47.27,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Apart from Yugi, there's someone else who has the Exodia card parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:54.36,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Indeed, the Exodia card parts is usually a rare card that is very hard to retrieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:58.82,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, I have 3 of each in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:01.28,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because of us Ghoul's tactics,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:04.45,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Getting a few rare cards is not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:05.66,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's lowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:11.16,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We Ghouls don't care what method we use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:11.96,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.50,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:31.06,Default,Ghoul,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll take your Red-Eyes Black Dragon now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.48,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Red... Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.03,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please open the door, Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka, Shizuka, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:48.03,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, No! Big brother didn't come, I'm not taking the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.50,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. Jounouchi-kun's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:55.75,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?! Jounouchi-kun didn't go to the hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:58.50,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How's that possible?! He was going there last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.17,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:03.26,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:09.72,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Honda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.81,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi, did Jounouchi really disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:15.73,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That idiot. What's he doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.77,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Honda, whats up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.44,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Borrowed it off my senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:22.57,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we need to search the streets, using it will be faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:27.20,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If Jounouchi-kun doesn't go to the hospital,  Shizuka-chan won't take the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.58,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me, that guy was in an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:35.25,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think the doctor who's doing the operation needs to go to America to operate on someone else tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:38.42,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If they don't start before noon then they won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.54,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.71,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright, let's split up and search!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.84,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:52.56,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.81,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're here, please reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:03.74,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That guy, he really disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.66,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.41,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.42,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Honda? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.00,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.05,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.55,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should be at the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.48,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jounouchi, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:40.52,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Last night when I was heading to the hospital, the Ghouls appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:41.73,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ghouls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:45.53,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A dark organization that hunts people's rare card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:49.70,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lost the Duel and Red-Eyes was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.49,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.70,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jounouchi, who cares about a simple {\i1}card{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.29,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}More importantly, you have to get to the hospital soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:58.67,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:03.34,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To me, Red-Eyes is the most important card for I need to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.17,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:06.55,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:11.34,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't go to the hospital, Shizuka-chan won't take her surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:15.02,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At important times like this, you should go and be there for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.18,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka-chan will then have more courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.39,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:24.11,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's useless, right now I can't comfort Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:29.86,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:32.91,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I enjoy watching you and and Yugi using cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:38.08,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I watch you guys play cards and your bond gets stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:46.96,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, because of a lost card, you want to lose your relationship with your only sister!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.14,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:06.82,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.65,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Honda-kun and... Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka! Open the door! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.74,Default,Doctor,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it's like this, I think it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:17.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:19.45,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}K-Katsuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:27.84,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mom, let me talk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.09,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka! Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.64,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka! Take the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.18,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.72,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No! Big brother is a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.81,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why didn't you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.81,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?! Why weren't you beside me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:46.19,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was afraid, so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:47.90,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:52.32,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I was coming yesterday, I bumped into something sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:58.24,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My brain was all empty, only thinking of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.66,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.58,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But my friend helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:08.13,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He kept on looking me, telling me about your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:13.72,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He let me know no matter how painful, how hateful it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:19.22,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I still can't forget those who need me, those who I worry for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:23.60,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The most important thing is the relationship between people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.56,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.19,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have forgotten about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:31.15,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope you won't be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:35.45,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No matter what time, we need to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.03,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:41.79,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:42.66,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.75,Default,Shizuka,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Katsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:55.47,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?! The surgery was a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.39,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.22,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.85,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\3c&H5C5C5C&}Jounouchi-kun, tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:05.35,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi, this upcoming Battle City is very terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:07.35,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\3c&H5C5C5C&}You've got to be careful. Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:11.27,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whats wrong, Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.86,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing, nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.07,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, I'll see you at Battle City!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.53,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.57,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Ghouls?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.62,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}What kind of people are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:22.91,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.08,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I'm not gonna involve you in my troubles anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:29.58,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I'll get Red-Eyes with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:40.09,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's finally here! Battle City's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:43.26,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At Kaiba-kun's luxurious opening session,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:47.06,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Powerful duelists all gathered and readied for battle in Domino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:53.36,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? The first battle in Battle City is the rare card hunter who stole Jounouchi's Red Eyes and Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:54.98,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do your best! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:56.82,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Defeat Jounouchi's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.61,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You must get Red-Eyes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.74,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next time! Fierce Fight! Battle City Begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:03.28,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:23:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here, always...
